{"tid":321095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【邊位巴打?】 銀行換鎖工人被困提款機 收據口遞紙仔求救","createTime":"2017-07-14T04:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T05:56:14.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"81123e2114b37c480d6ba3e86fe024d2a5ef8782","tid":321095,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:37:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/us/20170714/56953666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fus%2F20170714%2F56953666&d=674nXqZdAHT%2BHRUkGxEGD75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=8a82f578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fus%2F20170714%2F56953666&h=056055d2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/us/20170714/56953666</a><br />\n<br />\n「提款機是人扮的」這個笑話已經講了很久，但美國德州這部提款機內真的有人。一名外判工人在換鎖時被困在提款機房內，他卻沒有帶手機，只好從提款機收據口遞紙條出去，跟顧客求救。<br />\n<br />\n事發於科珀斯克里斯蒂市（Corpus Christi）一間美國銀行（Bank of America）分行。顧客收到的其中一張紙條寫道，「請救我。我被困在此。我沒有帶手機。請打給我老闆」，然後附上了一個電話號碼。<br />\n<br />\n有些顧客以為這是個惡作劇，幸好有人打電話報警，警員到場踢開門才救他出來，當時他已經被困兩小時。<br />\n<br />\n去救人的警員奧爾登（Richard Olden）也忍不住笑說：「我們聽到機器裏面傳出一點小聲音。你人生再也不會見到這樣的事了，某個人被困在ATM機內。太瘋狂了。」<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司"},{"pid":"49afee12bd77f64948692f301fca89013b9e3720","tid":321095,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:38:12.000Z","msg":"聰明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b5fab836c48c64b9bc2d8b2fb4c90f2c84c3a1","tid":321095,"uid":21480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:40:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5444d850aa74c046319a6fafba9f1df6f07858cd","tid":321095,"uid":24989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg